**Heir** | Attribute
__Basics__
Applied by the Monarch. Grants an additional vote on polls, and negates a vote.

__Formalized__
Passive Start Day:
  • Manipulate `Lynch` Poll (@Selection has `-1` votes) (~AttributePhase)
  • Manipulate `Election` Poll (@Selection has `-1` votes) (~AttributePhase)
  • Manipulate @Self's `special public voting power` to `1` (~AttributePhase)
